The San Benito CISD Board of Trustees and Superintendent of Schools Dr. Nate Carman are proud to announce the Top 10 Graduates for the San Benito High School Class of 2020:

1. Michael Dylan Thomas, Valedictorian;
2. Haley Lian Hernandez, Salutatorian;
3. Ayden Jay Soliz;
4. Katarina Lynn Guerra;
5. Angelin Starr Cruz;
6. Ariel Kristen Lopez;
7. Arturo Arratia, Jr.;
8. Jayson Bryan Martinez;
9. Connie Jaqueline Martinez Chavarria; and
10. Matthew Henry Guevara.

On behalf of the entire San Benito CISD family, CONGRATULATIONS to our San Benito High School Class of 2020 Top 10 Graduates as well as to their parents and families as they proudly share in this honor!

